field.comment:
Optional: When using custom sort-options, set the field name (used for sorting) and the Boxalino field, joined via a colon (:),
                               add a hyphen (-) and define the default order (asc, desc) each group is to be divided via a semicolon.
                               ex: custom_sort1:boxalino_field-asc;custom_sort2:boxalino_field-desc;

Optional: When using custom created properties that start with "products_" -- for SEO reasons.
                                Add the properties here divided by comma (,).
                                Use the SEO property/parameter view (ex: for "products_custom_field" write "custom_field");
